      "Text": "Security update for gstreamer-plugins-ugly",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gstreamer-plugins-ugly fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-2920: GStreamer ASF Demuxer Heap-based Buffer Overflow Remote Code Execution Vulnerability (bsc#1259367).\n- CVE-2026-2922: GStreamer RealMedia Demuxer Out-Of-Bounds Write Remote Code Execution Vulnerability (bsc#1259370).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
